Notebook[{
Cell["\<\
CVTPulley\[LongDash]Reproduce Table 3 and Figure 5
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9827697854986057`*^9, 3.9827698012484093`*^9}, {
  3.982821540885128*^9, 
  3.9828215409969254`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e6c7bacc-c32a-0d47-9fba-\
545eef6b787f"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook reproduces Table 3 and Figure 5 from the article.

It computes the midpoint value xi by midpoint iteration, constructs the
quadratic approximation of the symmetric solution, and compares it with the \
discrete symmetric profiles.

Before using this notebook, evaluate 00_LoadProject.nb so that the package
is loaded.
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.982769805044218*^9, 3.9827698411578865`*^9}, {
  3.9828215434772186`*^9, 
  3.9828215436047096`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8021c2c6-1a15-0d45-9b6d-\
6004869ae2e0"],

